snippet.title: Tricky Super Mario Bros. U - NSMBFMD Trailer
snippet.description:
This trailer for Tricky Super Mario Bros. U was featured in the New Super Mario Bros. Franchise Modding Direct. I never uploaded it because I expected it to take another form, but it never did... whoops. Regardless, here it is in its unlisted glory.

Trailer theme is “Boss Battle! (Bowser's Minions)” from Mario & Luigi: Superstar Saga + Bowser's Minions.

Be sure to check the New Super Mario Bros. Franchise Modding Direct, which is where this trailer originally premiered:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dvAH9bEEuPk
